      "text": "Another major drug bust through Operation Pacific Viper. \n\nThe crew of #USCG Cutter Tampa interdicted a go-fast vessel deep in the Eastern Pacific, seizing 1,925 kilograms of cocaine worth an estimated $31.9M. \n\nSince launching Operation Pacific Viper in early August, we’ve interdicted over 200K lbs of cocaine. As significant transport of illicit narcotics continues from South and Central America, our maritime fighting force remains focused on countering narco-terrorism and protecting the homeland.   \n\n#SemperParatus",
      "text_resolved": "Another major drug bust through Operation Pacific Viper. \n\nThe crew of #USCG Cutter Tampa interdicted a go-fast vessel deep in the Eastern Pacific, seizing 1,925 kilograms of cocaine worth an estimated $31.9M. \n\nSince launching Operation Pacific Viper in early August, we’ve interdicted over 200K lbs of cocaine. As significant transport of illicit narcotics continues from South and Central America, our maritime fighting force remains focused on countering narco-terrorism and protecting the homeland.   \n\n#SemperParatus",
